        <supports>Spell Saving Throw</supports>
        <description>
            <p>You summon 3 Multiples of yourself to distract enemies; each multiple increases your AC by 2. Each time
                an attack misses you, one multiple detonates, dealing 1d6 radiant damage and all creatures within 5 ft
                must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is blinded for 2 turns.
            </p>
        </description>
